Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白石兄！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要这个是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是白石稔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  接下来请欣赏
